---
import '../../styles/ebookv2.css';

const canonicalURL = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site);
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Global Metadata -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />

    <!-- Canonical URL -->
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalURL} />

    <!-- Primary Meta Tags -->
    <title>You Don’t Need JavaScript | Terms & Conditions</title>
    <meta name="title" content="You Don’t Need JavaScript | Terms & Conditions" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Discover tips, tricks and modern HTML & CSS features to create interactive components without JavaScript in this practical ebook."
    />

    <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={Astro.url} />
    <meta property="og:title" content="You Don’t Need JavaScript | Terms & Conditions" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="A practical ebook for front-end devs - Terms & Conditions" />
    <meta property="og:image" content={new URL('ebook.png', Astro.site)} />

    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta property="twitter:url" content={Astro.url} />
    <meta property="twitter:title" content="You Don’t Need JavaScript | Terms & Conditions" />
    <meta property="twitter:description" content="A practical ebook for front-end devs - Terms & Conditions" />
    <meta property="twitter:image" content={new URL('ebook.png', Astro.site)} />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <a href="/you-dont-need-js/">← Back to the ebook</a>
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>

      <p>Last updated: October 2025</p>

      <h2>1. General</h2>
      <p>
        This ebook, You Don’t Need JavaScript, is sold by Theo Soti (the “Author”). By purchasing or downloading this
        product, you agree to the following terms.
      </p>

      <h2>2. License & Usage</h2>
      <p>
        Your purchase grants you a personal, non-transferable license to access and read the ebook and any included
        materials. You may not redistribute, resell, or share the files publicly, whether in part or in full, without
        written permission from the author.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Delivery</h2>
      <p>
        After payment, you will receive immediate access to download the ebook and any associated files via the link
        provided at checkout or by email.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you’re not satisfied with your purchase for any reason, you can
        request a full refund within 30 days of your purchase date. If you experience any issue accessing the files,
        please contact us and we’ll make sure to help right away.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any question, please reach out at: <a href="mailto:hey@theosoti.com">hey@theosoti.com</a></p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
